ygData.subject: But They raised the Bar!
ygData.msgSnippet: Hail Fellow Tunesmiths, Kinda anti climatic now, but Ding! Welcome to L50. All I can say is get a group together and start on the first floor of Kedge at L35
ygData.messageBody:
Hail Fellow Tunesmiths,

Kinda anti climatic now, but Ding! Welcome to L50.
All I can say is get a group together and start on the first floor of Kedge
at L35 or so, and work your way through as you level up. The loot sucks, but
the respawn rate makes this about the fastest experience place we have ever
seen, and it's nearly always empty, even on Xegony.

Lady Brilinnia Ban'Sidhe
Knight Marshall, Order of the Rose
Excalibur, Xegony
